Name: 极限挑战（Challenge Of Limits）
About the game: This is an interesting variety of fun level series VR game, each game has a specific time system, players can complete the task in each game level. The game requires players to get scores and get different rewards within a specified period of time. Different series of games bring different tasks. Extreme challenge will launch different series and extreme tasks for you to challenge in the future. Thank you for coming new Pacific battle game new servant game new game hall
